long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Mood Start is a Chrome extension that replaces the default new tab page with a beautiful, calming landscape wallpaper. The extension has been designed to promote a sense of peace and motivation, helping users to start their day on a positive note. Each time a new tab is opened, the extension will randomly select a new wallpaper from a curated collection of peaceful landscapes, which can include images of mountains, forests, beaches, and more.

Users should install Mood Start if they are looking for a simple and effective way to improve their mood and productivity. The extension's peaceful wallpapers can help to reduce stress and anxiety, and promote a sense of calm and well-being. Additionally, Mood Start can also serve as a source of inspiration, helping users to stay motivated and focused throughout the day. With its easy installation and customizable settings, Mood Start is a great tool for anyone looking to improve their mental and emotional well-being.
